---
title: Smart Moroccan-Style Tilapia Fillets   with Cilantro-Yogurt Dressing and Couscous
description: Tender tilapia and a medley of veggies are seasoned with fragrant Harissa Spice Blend, then topped off with a dreamy herb-yogurt dressing and crispy shallots for layers of texture and flavour. It's a cozy meal perfect for any night of the week.

